&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Summerhill Services Ltd is a subsidiary of Birmingham &amp; Solihull Mental Health Foundation Trust, focusing on delivering the highest standard of service to the Trust through our well established facilities department, an opportunity has become available and we are looking to employ a self motivated individual to work as part of the Domestic Team working at the Reaside Clinic, Great Park Rubery B45 9BE. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The successful applicant will be expected to work in all areas of the Secure Mental Health Facility; including Patients Bedrooms , corridors, entrances, bathroom &amp; toilets, Clinic rooms and admin areas and must be able to work alone or as part of a team under the supervision of the Domestic Supervisor. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
